question:
District category contains Medical District, Senior Living Community, Legal District, and High-rise Apartment Complex.
Supermarkets category contains Lidl, Auchan, Food 4 Less, and Blue Apron.
Product category contains Pizza Dough, Canned Mushrooms, Alcoholic Beverages, and Pudding.
The number of each Legal District 's Lidl equals the sum of each Food 4 Less 's Canned Mushrooms, each Lidl 's Pudding, and each Legal District 's Auchan.
The number of each Legal District 's Auchan equals 5.
The number of each Food 4 Less 's Canned Mushrooms equals 20 times each Legal District 's Auchan.
The number of each Auchan 's Canned Mushrooms equals the difference of each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Auchan and each Auchan 's Alcoholic Beverages.
The number of each Medical District 's Auchan equals each Auchan 's Product.
The number of each Blue Apron 's Pizza Dough equals 1 more than the difference of each Auchan 's Alcoholic Beverages and each Senior Living Community 's Blue Apron.
The number of each Lidl 's Pizza Dough equals the difference of each Senior Living Community 's Lidl and each Medical District 's Auchan.
The number of each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Auchan equals 10.
The number of each Lidl 's Pudding equals 11.
The number of each Medical District 's Blue Apron equals 12.
The number of each Auchan 's Alcoholic Beverages equals each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Auchan.
The number of each Blue Apron 's Canned Mushrooms equals 11 more than the sum of each Medical District 's Auchan and each Auchan 's Canned Mushrooms.
The number of each Senior Living Community 's Blue Apron equals 4 more than the difference of each Medical District 's Auchan and each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Auchan.
The number of each Legal District 's Food 4 Less equals each Auchan 's Alcoholic Beverages.
The number of each Medical District 's Food 4 Less equals each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Supermarkets.
The number of each Senior Living Community 's Lidl equals 18 more than each Blue Apron 's Product.
How many Supermarkets does Senior Living Community have?
solution:
Define each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Auchan as M; So M = 10.
Define each Auchan 's Alcoholic Beverages as K; So K = M = 10.
Define each Auchan 's Canned Mushrooms as W; So W = M - K = 10 - 0 = 0.
Define each Auchan 's Product as a; So a = W + K = 0 + 0 = 0.
Define each Medical District 's Auchan as k; So k = a = 0.
Define each Senior Living Community 's Blue Apron as A; W = k - M = 0 - 10 = 13; So A = 4 + W = 4 + 13 = 17.
Define each Blue Apron 's Canned Mushrooms as j; A = k + W = 0 + 13 = 13; So j = 11 + A = 11 + 13 = 1.
Define each Blue Apron 's Pizza Dough as r; q = K - A = 0 - 13 = 10; So r = 1 + q = 1 + 10 = 11.
Define each Blue Apron 's Product as Q; So Q = j + r = 1 + 11 = 12.
Define each Senior Living Community 's Lidl as B; So B = 18 + Q = 18 + 12 = 7.
Define each Senior Living Community 's Supermarkets as E; So E = A + B = 13 + 7 = 20.
